---
import Page from "@/src/layouts/Page.astro"
---

<Page class="max-w-7xl">

	<div class="space-y-4">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-8xl mb-12">Sangwu Lee</h1>
		<div class="font-serif space-y-20">
			<div id="abstract">
				<h2 class="md:text-4xl mb-4">Abstract</h2>
				<div class="md:text-3xl my-2">
					<p class="leading-normal">
						Hi, I teach machines to draw pretty pictures.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="background">
				<h3 class="md:text-3xl mb-4">Background</h3>
				<div class="md:text-2xl my-2">
					<p class="leading-normal">
						Currently, I'm working at <a href="krea.ai">krea</a> where I teach machines to draw pretty pictures.
						Previsouly, I was founding engineer at <a href="https://oleve.co">Oleve</a> where I helped scale consumer products.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="appendix">
				<h3 class="md:text-2xl mb-4">Appendix</h3>
				<div class="md:text-xl my-2">
					<p> - The first neural network I've ever trained was a restricted Boltzmann machine.</p>
					<p> - From 2016 - 2024, I mostly lived in a dorm room and barracks.</p>
					<p> - I learned C with <a href="https://www.aladin.co.kr/shop/wproduct.aspx?ItemId=8016119&ptid=5">this lovely book.</a></p>
