					<p> - Yes, I've already finished my military service.</p>
					<p> - I went to a strange school called UWC-USA in Las Vegas, New Mexico.</p>
					<p> - I'm love <a href="https://github.com/jax-ml/jax">JAX</a>. I've used it train <a href="https://github.com/RE-N-Y/scratchpad">StyleGAN, ViT-VQGAN, EDM, and MaskGiT models on TPUv3 cluster</a>.</p>
					<p> - This site is built using <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a>.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		

	</div>

</Page>
